<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Privacy Policy - ClipHub</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/mobile.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-black text-white min-h-screen">
  <%- include('../partials/header') %>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Page Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500 to-red-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
          Privacy Policy
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-400">Last updated: October 19, 2025</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-8">
        <!-- Introduction -->
        <section class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#E31E24] mb-4">1. Introduction</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            ClipHub ("we", "us", or "our") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our platform. Please read this policy carefully to understand our views and practices regarding your personal data.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Information We Collect -->
        <section class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#E31E24] mb-4">2. Information We Collect</h2>
          <div class="text-gray-300 space-y-4">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-red-300 mb-2">2.1 Discord Account Information</h3>
              <p>When you authenticate with Discord, we collect:</p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4 mt-2">
                <li>Discord user ID</li>
                <li>Username and discriminator</li>
                <li>Avatar URL</li>
                <li>Email address (if provided)</li>
                <li>Server membership information</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-red-300 mb-2">2.2 Social Media Account Information</h3>
              <p>When you link your social media accounts, we collect:</p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4 mt-2">
                <li>Account handles and URLs (YouTube, TikTok, Instagram)</li>
                <li>Public profile information</li>
                <li>Video view counts and analytics</li>
                <li>Account verification status</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-red-300 mb-2">2.3 Submission and Campaign Data</h3>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4">
                <li>Video links and content submissions</li>
                <li>Analytics screenshots and proof</li>
                <li>View tracking data</li>
                <li>Earnings and payout information</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-red-300 mb-2">2.4 Automatically Collected Information</h3>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4">
                <li>IP address and browser information</li>
                <li>Session data and cookies</li>
                <li>Usage statistics and activity logs</li>
                <li>Device and operating system information</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- How We Use Your Information -->
        <section class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#E31E24] mb-4">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <div class="text-gray-300">
            <p class="mb-3">We use the collected information for the following purposes:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
              <li>To provide, operate, and maintain our platform</li>
              <li>To authenticate and verify user accounts</li>
              <li>To process campaign submissions and track performance</li>
              <li>To calculate earnings and process payouts</li>
              <li>To detect and prevent fraudulent activity</li>
              <li>To communicate with you about campaigns, updates, and support</li>
              <li>To improve our services and user experience</li>
              <li>To comply with legal obligations and enforce our terms</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Data Sharing and Disclosure -->
        <section class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#E31E24] mb-4">4. Data Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
          <div class="text-gray-300 space-y-3">
            <p><strong>4.1 Campaign Sponsors:</strong> We may share your username, submission data, and view counts with campaign sponsors for verification and payment purposes.</p>
            <p><strong>4.2 Service Providers:</strong> We use third-party services (Discord, YouTube API, TikTok API, Instagram API) to operate our platform. These providers have their own privacy policies.</p>
            <p><strong>4.3 Legal Requirements:</strong> We may disclose your information if required by law, court order, or governmental authority.</p>
            <p><strong>4.4 Business Transfers:</strong> In the event of a merger, acquisition, or sale of assets, your information may be transferred to the new owner.</p>
            <p><strong>We do not sell your personal information to third parties.</strong></p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Data Security -->
        <section class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#E31E24] mb-4">5. Data Security</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your data, including encryption, secure authentication, and access controls. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure. While we strive to protect your information, we cannot guarantee absolute security.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Data Retention -->
        <section class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#E31E24] mb-4">6. Data Retention</h2>
          <div class="text-gray-300 space-y-3">
            <p>We retain your data for as long as necessary to provide our services and comply with legal obligations:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
              <li><strong>Account Data:</strong> Retained while your account is active</li>
              <li><strong>Submission Data:</strong> Retained for 3 years for audit and payment verification</li>
              <li><strong>Payout Records:</strong> Retained for 7 years for tax and legal compliance</li>
              <li><strong>Analytics Data:</strong> Retained for 1 year for performance tracking</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Your Rights -->
        <section class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#E31E24] mb-4">7. Your Rights</h2>
          <div class="text-gray-300">
            <p class="mb-3">Depending on your jurisdiction, you may have the following rights:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
              <li><strong>Access:</strong> Request a copy of your personal data</li>
              <li><strong>Correction:</strong> Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
              <li><strong>Deletion:</strong> Request deletion of your data (subject to legal requirements)</li>
              <li><strong>Portability:</strong> Request transfer of your data to another service</li>
              <li><strong>Objection:</strong> Object to certain data processing activities</li>
              <li><strong>Withdraw Consent:</strong> Withdraw consent for data processing at any time</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-4">To exercise these rights, contact us through our Discord server.</p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Cookies and Tracking -->
        <section class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#E31E24] mb-4">8. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
          <div class="text-gray-300 space-y-3">
            <p>We use cookies and similar tracking technologies to:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
              <li>Maintain your login session</li>
              <li>Remember your preferences</li>
              <li>Analyze usage patterns and improve our service</li>
              <li>Prevent fraud and ensure security</li>
            </ul>
            <p>You can control cookies through your browser settings, but disabling cookies may limit platform functionality.</p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Third-Party Links -->
        <section class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#E31E24] mb-4">9. Third-Party Links</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            Our platform may contain links to third-party websites and services (Discord, YouTube, TikTok, Instagram). We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these third parties. Please review their privacy policies before providing any personal information.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Children's Privacy -->
        <section class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#E31E24] mb-4">10. Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            Our platform is not intended for children under 18. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you are a parent or guardian and believe your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us immediately.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Changes to This Policy -->
        <section class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#E31E24] mb-4">11. Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of significant changes via email or Discord notification. Your continued use of the platform after changes indicates acceptance of the updated policy.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Contact Us -->
        <section class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#E31E24] mb-4">12. Contact Us</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us through our Discord server:
          </p>
          <a href="https://discord.gg/GpwemE5Edg" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-[#E31E24] hover:bg-[#B91419] text-white font-semibold rounded-lg transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M20.317 4.37a19.791 19.791 0 0 0-4.885-1.515a.074.074 0 0 0-.079.037c-.21.375-.444.864-.608 1.25a18.27 18.27 0 0 0-5.487 0a12.64 12.64 0 0 0-.617-1.25a.077.077 0 0 0-.079-.037A19.736 19.736 0 0 0 3.677 4.37a.07.07 0 0 0-.032.027C.533 9.046-.32 13.58.099 18.057a.082.082 0 0 0 .031.057a19.9 19.9 0 0 0 5.993 3.03a.078.078 0 0 0 .084-.028a14.09 14.09 0 0 0 1.226-1.994a.076.076 0 0 0-.041-.106a13.107 13.107 0 0 1-1.872-.892a.077.077 0 0 1-.008-.128a10.2 10.2 0 0 0 .372-.292a.074.074 0 0 1 .077-.01c3.928 1.793 8.18 1.793 12.062 0a.074.074 0 0 1 .078.01c.12.098.246.198.373.292a.077.077 0 0 1-.006.127a12.299 12.299 0 0 1-1.873.892a.077.077 0 0 0-.041.107c.36.698.772 1.362 1.225 1.993a.076.076 0 0 0 .084.028a19.839 19.839 0 0 0 6.002-3.03a.077.077 0 0 0 .032-.054c.5-5.177-.838-9.674-3.549-13.66a.061.061 0 0 0-.031-.03zM8.02 15.33c-1.183 0-2.157-1.085-2.157-2.419c0-1.333.956-2.419 2.157-2.419c1.21 0 2.176 1.096 2.157 2.42c0 1.333-.956 2.418-2.157 2.418zm7.975 0c-1.183 0-2.157-1.085-2.157-2.419c0-1.333.955-2.419 2.157-2.419c1.21 0 2.176 1.096 2.157 2.42c0 1.333-.946 2.418-2.157 2.418z"/>
            </svg>
            Contact Support
          </a>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
